## Analysis Instructions
1. Check if the code structure matches the defined architecture patterns
2. Verify that new components are placed in the correct modules/packages
3. Check for violations of layering rules (e.g., UI accessing DB directly)
4. Verify dependency direction (dependencies should flow toward stability)
5. Check that new code uses the team's designated patterns (e.g., repository pattern, factory, etc.)

